  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Historical Fashion Dress Up is a game that lets you explore fashion in Europe throughout history! The available fashion packs at this moment are 1680s, 1780s and 1820s. With more to come!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/5651b08b144045f000633dfb41486860.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/6d73df45f2cc97dd1702eaa04111d6bf.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/6d73df45f2cc97dd1702eaa04111d6bf.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every garment is researched and based on museum collections and contemporary art, offering an authentic experience of each era's style. You can also read more about historical fashion in our info menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/a906555caf326f336b55f2eaf0ca0261.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ff75ce3cb3df5e015b702d459bad859d.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ff75ce3cb3df5e015b702d459bad859d.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the appearance of your characters. Experiment with facial features, hairstyles, accessories, and more to bring your character to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/7068677f8cef6b7e411b15f74421f011.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/5cde498c7931172fa77f06c0e0aa9959.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/5cde498c7931172fa77f06c0e0aa9959.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/5cde498c7931172fa77f06c0e0aa9959.mp4?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Save screenshots of your favorite characters and outfits. Share your creations with friends or use them as inspiration for your next design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/466d656c3b39934e4d45fd5478abe26a.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/4b5ad8cc8e4aa374e10691f68331bd7a.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/4b5ad8cc8e4aa374e10691f68331bd7a.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/4b5ad8cc8e4aa374e10691f68331bd7a.mp4?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bring your digital creations to life by printing out your characters as charming paper dolls. Print in color, or color the dolls yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/efb233c18ea37d743becc1d9f9b71bda.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ea72ab3f8dedd5f8ba5f8e9003115038.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ea72ab3f8dedd5f8ba5f8e9003115038.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ea72ab3f8dedd5f8ba5f8e9003115038.mp4?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill your wardrobe with all your favorite outfits and save them for later.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/c47d3a03dd62d79f2c326c7bfa2e5593.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/57a8c5dfb4005d77f44a3bd6c8b5cc12.webp?t=1769769379\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/57a8c5dfb4005d77f44a3bd6c8b5cc12.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=658 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is designed for those seeking a relaxing experience while also learning a thing or two about historical fashion. Or for all the fashion enthusiasts out there wanting to dive into the details of historical fashion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your inner fashion designer and relive the grace and style of past fashions. Whether you're a history enthusiast or a fashion lover, this is where you can create, explore, and appreciate fashion throughout history!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Historical Fashion Dress Up is a game that lets you explore fashion in Europe throughout history! The available fashion packs at this moment are 1680s, 1780s and 1820s. With more to come!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/5651b08b144045f000633dfb41486860.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/6d73df45f2cc97dd1702eaa04111d6bf.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/6d73df45f2cc97dd1702eaa04111d6bf.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every garment is researched and based on museum collections and contemporary art, offering an authentic experience of each era's style. You can also read more about historical fashion in our info menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/a906555caf326f336b55f2eaf0ca0261.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ff75ce3cb3df5e015b702d459bad859d.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ff75ce3cb3df5e015b702d459bad859d.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the appearance of your characters. Experiment with facial features, hairstyles, accessories, and more to bring your character to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/7068677f8cef6b7e411b15f74421f011.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/5cde498c7931172fa77f06c0e0aa9959.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/5cde498c7931172fa77f06c0e0aa9959.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/5cde498c7931172fa77f06c0e0aa9959.mp4?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Save screenshots of your favorite characters and outfits. Share your creations with friends or use them as inspiration for your next design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/466d656c3b39934e4d45fd5478abe26a.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/4b5ad8cc8e4aa374e10691f68331bd7a.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/4b5ad8cc8e4aa374e10691f68331bd7a.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/4b5ad8cc8e4aa374e10691f68331bd7a.mp4?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Bring your digital creations to life by printing out your characters as charming paper dolls. Print in color, or color the dolls yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/efb233c18ea37d743becc1d9f9b71bda.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ea72ab3f8dedd5f8ba5f8e9003115038.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ea72ab3f8dedd5f8ba5f8e9003115038.webm?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/ea72ab3f8dedd5f8ba5f8e9003115038.mp4?t=1769769379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill your wardrobe with all your favorite outfits and save them for later.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/c47d3a03dd62d79f2c326c7bfa2e5593.avif?t=1769769379\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/57a8c5dfb4005d77f44a3bd6c8b5cc12.webp?t=1769769379\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2692430/extras/57a8c5dfb4005d77f44a3bd6c8b5cc12.poster.avif?t=1769769379\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=658 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is designed for those seeking a relaxing experience while also learning a thing or two about historical fashion. Or for all the fashion enthusiasts out there wanting to dive into the details of historical fashion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your inner fashion designer and relive the grace and style of past fashions. Whether you're a history enthusiast or a fashion lover, this is where you can create, explore, and appreciate fashion throughout history!</p>",
